{{Infobox tornado year |name = Tornadoes of 1965 |image = |caption = |timespan = January 8–December 23, 1965 |max_F = F5 |max_location = [[Colome, South Dakota|Colome, SD]] |max_date = May 8 |tornadoes_usa = 897<ref>http://www.tornadohistoryproject.com/tornado/1965/map</ref> |total_damages_usa = Unknown |total_fatalities_usa= 301 |total_fatalities_world = >301 |year=1965 }}
This page documents the '''[[tornado]]es and [[tornado outbreak]]s of 1965''', primarily in the United States. Most tornadoes form in the U.S., although some events may take place internationally. Tornado statistics for older years like this often appear significantly lower than modern years due to fewer reports or confirmed tornadoes. {{Clear}}
