ng-pl|Zespół Elektrociepłowni w Łodzi}}), also known under the company name of '''Veolia Energia Łódź S.A.''' are [[combined heat and power station]]s in [[Łódź]], [[Poland]]. They are operated by [[Veolia Energia Łódź]].
